  "datePublished": "2026-03-06",
  "description": "The ***plain language movement*** is an ongoing effort — spanning government, legal, medical, and technical communication — to make public-facing documents understandable by the people they affect. The movement treats clear communication not as a stylistic preference but as a matter of access and rights.",
